Package: glotte
Type: Package
Title: This package with the discourse data of the GloUrb project and interacts with the GloUrb DataBase.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lise Vaudor
Maintainer: Lise Vaudor <lise.vaudor@ens-lyon.fr>
Description: This package interacts with the discourses-related tables in the GloUrb project DataBase to 1) get the data and 2) produce plots. It is used in the GloUrb application but can also be used through a regular R session.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
